     `on_domain_loaded` / `reacquire` / `blocking_holder` / `list_all` and into
     `_shape` / `_none` (new optional `ttl_s` param) so the store calls and the
     client `lease_ttl_s` hint use one resolved value. Refreshed the module
     docstring's lease paragraph.
3. `src/back/objects/domain/SettingsService.py`
   - Added `get_edit_lock_ttl_result` (returns the effective TTL via
     `EditLockService._ttl_seconds`) and `save_edit_lock_ttl_result`
